OL,3,CEngland face reigning champions
OL,4,CArgentina in World Cup semi-final
OL,6,FFor England fans and the players,
OL,7,Fvictory tonight will mean a chance to
OL,8,Fend the 60-year wait for glory, as ITV
OL,9,FNews Sports Editor Steve Scott reports
OL,10,Ffrom Atlanta
OL,12,FEngland are gearing up to play
OL,13,FArgentina for a spot in the World Cup
OL,14,Ffinal on Sunday.
OL,16,FThis is only the fourth time the Three
OL,17,FLions have made it to the semi-finals,
OL,18,Fhaving qualified in 1990 and 2018, and
OL,19,Fonly reaching the final in the triumph
OL,20,Fof 1966.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
