OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784231285
OL,3,CEngland face reigning champions
OL,4,CArgentina in World Cup semi-final
OL,6,FEngland and Argentina will play at the
OL,7,FMercedes-Benz Stadium in Atlanta,
OL,8,FGeorgia, at 8pm BST.
OL,10,FThundery showers are predicted for
OL,11,FWednesday in the capital. Normally,
OL,12,Fthis would risk triggering Fifa's
OL,13,Fthunderstorm protocol, but the stadium
OL,14,Fhas a retractable roof, so the game
OL,15,Fwill not be impacted.
OL,17,FThe stadium is also air-conditioned,
OL,18,Fallowing the players to play at
OL,19,Foptimal temperature conditions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
