CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784231285
OL,3,CEngland face reigning champions
OL,4,CArgentina in World Cup semi-final
OL,6,FDuring England's game against Norway
OL,7,Fin Miami, both sides appeared sluggish
OL,8,Fat times as they battled temperatures
OL,9,Fabove 30C and high humidity.
OL,11,FReigning champions Argentina have
OL,12,Flifted the World Cup trophy three
OL,13,Ftimes - in 1978, 1986 and 2022 - while
OL,14,Fso far England have only clinched the
OL,15,Ftitle once.
OL,17,FHeading into the semis, Argentina are
OL,18,Fsecond in Fifa's World Cup goal
OL,19,Frankings, having scored 17 times in
OL,20,Fthis tournament. England are fourth,
OL,21,Fwith 13 goals.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
