PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784231285
OL,3,CEngland face reigning champions
OL,4,CArgentina in World Cup semi-final
OL,6,FIf England are successful, they will
OL,7,Fface Spain on Sunday after the
OL,8,FSpaniards secured their place in the
OL,9,Ffinal with a decisive 2-0 victory over
OL,10,Ftournament favourites France on
OL,11,FTuesday.
OL,13,FAfter several games at unsociable
OL,14,Fhours, the 8pm kick-off will likely
OL,15,Fmake England's match one of the most-
OL,16,Fwatched football matches in years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
