OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784231285
OL,3,CEngland face reigning champions
OL,4,CArgentina in World Cup semi-final
OL,6,FPubs in England are expecting to sell
OL,7,Fsix million extra pints on Wednesday
OL,8,Fevening, according to the British Beer
OL,9,Fand Pub Association (BBPA), 75% more
OL,10,Fthan usual for the middle of the week.
OL,12,FDespite the significant historical
OL,13,Fcontext behind the game, both sides
OL,14,Fhave said they are focused on playing
OL,15,Ffootball over politics.
OL,17,FArgentina boss Lionel Scaloni said
OL,18,Frecently it would be wrong to make the
OL,19,Fgame about the Falklands War.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784231285
OL,3,CEngland face reigning champions
OL,4,CArgentina in World Cup semi-final
OL,6,F"It's a football match; I can't mix
OL,7,Fthings up, out of respect for what
OL,8,Fhappened so many years ago," he said.
OL,10,F"It was a very sad time in our
OL,11,Fhistory, and there isn't much we can
OL,12,Fdo about it. Mixing the two would be
OL,13,Fmadness. We criticise that there was
OL,14,Fwar."
OL,16,FEngland manager Thomas Tuchel said:
OL,17,F"We respect our opponent, but we don't
OL,18,Fdip in historic events and we don't
OL,19,Fmake it bigger than it is."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@\O]rD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
