PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784231285
OL,3,CEngland face reigning champions
OL,4,CArgentina in World Cup semi-final
OL,6,FWhen asked, the manager, who took over
OL,7,Ffrom Gareth Southgate in 2024, said he
OL,8,Fdoes not feel burdened by England's 60-
OL,9,Fyear wait to reclaim the World Cup
OL,10,Ftitle.
OL,12,FHe replied: "There's so much to love
OL,13,Fabout this England squad and our team
OL,14,Fthat I'm very glad that people feel it.
OL,16,F"A burden? No, I don't feel a burden.
OL,17,FI mean, we feel the tension and I will
OL,18,Fbe nervous, and of course that is that
OL,19,Fis normal.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784231285
OL,3,CEngland face reigning champions
OL,4,CArgentina in World Cup semi-final
OL,6,F"But I feel no burden. I feel what I
OL,7,Freally like is what I feel in the last
OL,8,Fdays that the players are very, very
OL,9,Fcompetitive.
OL,11,FTuchel also sought to rubbish claims
OL,12,Fthere was a rift between him and Jude
OL,13,FBellingham.
OL,15,FHe told talkSPORT: "I wonder who blows
OL,16,Fthese things up, eh? So, there is
OL,17,Fnothing to blow up and if it's blown
OL,18,Fup, it's blown up in the media, of
OL,19,Fcourse."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
