OL,3,CEngland face reigning champions
OL,4,CArgentina in World Cup semi-final
OL,6,FHe added: "You try to blow it up and
OL,7,Fpeople try to create misunderstandings
OL,8,Fand cracks where no cracks are."
OL,10,FYou can watch England v Argentina on
OL,11,Fthe BBC at 8pm on Wednesday.
